 Complete the phrase â€œbread and â€¦.â€ - thatâ€™s <em>System1</em> at work.
 Count the occurrences of letter â€˜aâ€™ in the next page - that is our <em>System2</em>.
 Dr. Kahneman talks about all the topics mentioned above from <em>Human Irrationality</em> to
 <em>Hedonic Psychology</em> in a very interesting and conversational tone. This book is not
