<h3 id="the-pragmatic-programmer-by-andrew-hunt-dave-thomas"><strong>The Pragmatic Programmer</strong> by <em>Andrew Hunt, Dave Thomas</em></h3>
<p>â€œTo err is to humanâ€. As human beings, we are susceptible to mistakes.
This holds true even for software programmers. Some mistakes are grave and put us in
